VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT BinaryFormatter\s*\(\s*\)|new\s+BinaryFormatter|BinaryFormatter\.Deserialize\s*\(
WHEN EXPR MISSING:SerializationBinder|AllowType|TypeNameHandling\.None|Activator\.CreateInstance && MISSING:test|example
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects use of BinaryFormatter, which is insecure and produces deserialization gadget chains.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for Insecure Deserialization: BinaryFormatter.
